            "image_border_color": "#ffffff"
          }
        },
        "bullet_fDftmA": {
          "type": "bullet",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Korean-Inspired Skincare Formula</strong> - We don’t just add “collagen” for the label—our mask is infused with low molecular weight hydrolyzed collagen and probiotics (Galactomyces ferment filtrate), ingredients that are backed by dermatological research for visible skin hydration, firmness, and resilience. This formula is designed to mimic the results seen in clinical skin studies.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "bullet_xWWenL": {
          "type": "bullet",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Enhanced Absorption with Hydrogel Technology </strong>- Unlike thin cotton masks that dry out quickly, our unique jelly-like hydrogel texture locks in serum and molds to your skin for maximum contact. This ensures deep penetration of active ingredients and prevents quick evaporation—so your skin can drink in every drop of hydration.</p>"
          }
        },
        "bullet_9F8GB3": {
          "type": "bullet",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Sourced for Purity & Potency</strong> - <br/>Our mask is produced under strict quality standards, formulated without parabens, sulfates, artificial dyes, or harsh preservatives. Only skin-loving ingredients are included to target hydration, plumping, and smoothing.</p>"
          }
        },
        "bullet_B8LpEK": {
          "type": "bullet",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Inspired by skincare professionals</strong> - this mask blends scientific formulation with the experience of thousands of customers, helping skin appear more hydrated, visibly plumper-looking, and radiantly healthy after every use.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
